data.description: Custom built home on corner double lot with four bedrooms - all with walk in closets, two bathrooms, a living area, breakfast area, formal dining area and a gourmet kitchen.  The kitchen features custom wood cabinetry, granite counters and a tiled backsplash with an island.  There is a nice bar area for additional seating or for serving food and the living room is open to the kitchen and dining area. Primary bedroom is oversized with tray ceilings, a HUGE walk in closet and a large bathroom with enormous tiled shower with 2 shower heads, double vanities and a make up area. The indoor laundry room has lots of cabinet space and is located right next to the two car garage with garage door opener. This home has been well maintained and is move in ready.Solar panels will be paid at closing by seller.
